          </div>
        </div>
        <p><em><strong>Table 1</strong>: Proxy IP addresses found in DOM of “Booking-Mailer V2.2” tool (Source: Recorded Future)</em></p>
        <p>Insikt Group identified additional instances of the Phishing Email Management Tooling, all hosted on IP addresses announced by the same set of Autonomous Systems (ASes). The identified IP addresses are listed in <strong>Table 2</strong>. The domains hosted on these IP addresses are listed in <strong>Appendix H</strong>.</p>
